      • query_ForValidReceiver_ShouldReceive200_ShouldReceiveValidResponse

        public void query_ForValidReceiver_ShouldReceive200_ShouldReceiveValidResponse(String receiverName,
                                                                               String receiverURI)
                                                                        throws Exception
        For a valid receiver, this test checks for a return status code of 200 and the below fields in Json response are validated.
        • address - contains text that has parameter receiverName
        • imageUrl - contains text that has parameter receiverName
        • name - contains text that has parameter receiverName
        • currencySymbol - equals to "$"
        • type - equals to "payee"
        • currencyCode - equals to "USD"
        • status - does not have any value, is null
        • amount - does not have any value, is null
        • invoiceInfo - does not have any value, is null
        Parameters:
        receiverName - Name of the valid receiver
        receiverURI - URI of the receiver
        Throws:
        Exception
